ng. This women&amp;rsquo;s fringed leather <br />jacket back length (from collar to hem) measures 21 1/2&amp;quot;. Sizes: <br />S(4-6), M(8-10), L(12-14), XL(16-18), 2XL(20).&nbsp;</a></span></p>', 's7d9.scene7.com/is/image/sheplers/225a23_70_p1', '27');
